  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bc8 \u0baf\u0bc2\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe \u0b89\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd 40 \u0b86\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb0\u0bc2\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba9\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0baf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bc1 -\u00a0\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bb9\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bc0\u0bb0",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A bag of urea fertilizer is sold at Rs 40,000 - Agriculture Minister Mahinda Amaraweera",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Out of the 65,000 metric tons of urea fertilizer to be imported from Oman under the Indian loan program, the first phase of 40,000 metric tons of urea fertilizer will reach the country on 08th.",
        "A bag of urea will be distributed through the Department of Agriculture at Rs 10,000. Agriculture Minister Mahinda Amaraweera informed the House that the National Agriculture Policy Plan will be submitted in full within the next 03 months.",
        "The speaker stated the above while replying to oral questions raised by United People's Shakti member Kayanta Karunathilakka during the sitting of Parliament on Monday (04).",
        "The report submitted on the National Agricultural Policy Plan is being considered by key ministries including the Finance Ministry.",
        "I expect to present the National Agriculture Policy Plan to all 225 Members of Parliament within the next 03 months.",
        "Agricultural policy should be seen as stable. Agriculture policy should not change when government and ministers change.",
        "The change in agricultural policy is seen as a contributing factor to the current crisis.",
        "It has been decided to import 65,000 metric tons of fertilizer from Oman under the Indian loan scheme.",
        "Initially, 40,000 metric tons of fertilizer will arrive in the country on the 8th and the fertilizer will be distributed on the 9th and 10th through the Department of Agriculture and District Secretariat units.",
        "In the face of shortage of fertilizer, one block of urea fertilizer is being sold for 40,000 rupees.",
        "10,000 will be distributed to farmers through the Department of Agriculture through the Department of Agriculture.",
        "An excess of 25,000 metric tonnes of fertilizer imported under the loan scheme will be distributed to farmers engaged in maize cultivation.",
        "Adequate measures have been taken to obtain better yields in mass cultivation. He said that if Perumpogam succeeds, there will be no need to import rice. Fertilizer shortage will be solved in the future."
      ],
